<li><a href="http://www.freewritingadvice.com/articles/index_files/69techcomm.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.freewritingadvice.com/articles/index_files/69techcomm.htm" rel="nofollow">Technical Communicators: What's in a Name?</a></li>
