<li><a href="http://expertechwritersince2004.spaces.live.com/" class="external text" title="http://expertechwritersince2004.spaces.live.com/" rel="nofollow">An Expert in Technical Writing</a> is a discussion forum technical writers to help each other widen their technical horizons.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.hci.com.au/iso/" class="external text" title="http://www.hci.com.au/iso/" rel="nofollow">Standard for technical writers from ISO</a> Contact page for International Standards Organization working group for technical documentation standards</li>
